{"tid":977023,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我覺得5年來有藥KO 沙士係無可能...因為有伊波拉病毒","createTime":"2019-01-11T00:53:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-11T00:55:44.000Z","uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1ee654b51243eb7d2de87136d2fbdbf26f09fab7","tid":977023,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T00:53:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2234eae823778942f9d6ab6f0daba3c568baa668","tid":977023,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T00:55:44.000Z","msg":"【香港勁揪】可治療流感沙士 袁國勇研「超級萬用藥」最快5年內面世<br />\n<br />\n傳統的抗病毒藥物如利巴韋林、特敏福，是透過抑制病毒的DNA或蛋白，阻止其繁殖，爭取時間讓人體免疫系統擊退病毒。不過港大醫學院微生物學講座教授袁國勇參與的一項研究發現，只要阻截病毒吸收身體細胞的脂肪酸，病毒就失去複製、擴散到腦部等其他器官的能力。這項全新機制將可發展成醫治流行性感冒、腸病毒以至沙士、「新沙士」等多種致命傳染病的「超級萬用藥」，袁國勇稱，新藥最快5至8年內可以面世<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}